summary: Adds a small world space called Dovahkiin Hold.
descriptionHtml:
Dovahkiin Hold v0.0.62


This mod is in the very early stages of development. I only put in up in hope of getting some early feedback so I can make it as good as possible.  



===========================================================
What it is
===========================================================

This mod adds a new world space to Skyrim called Dovahkiin Hold. There is currently a keep, village, waterfall, river, lake, and some landscaping done in the village.  

coc DHOrigin

Comments, criticisms, suggestions, ideas, etc are very welcome.  



===========================================================
To Do
===========================================================

Too much to list at this time.  



===========================================================
Done
===========================================================

-Terrain, mountains, waterfall, river, lake.  
-Placed village buildings and Keep.  
-Landscaped village.  
-Footpaths, bridges done.  
-Main road 50%.  
-Placed stables.
